    "attributes": {
        "action": "Allow courts to find executors who fail to perform their duties in contempt",
        "additional_details": "Otherwise, solicitors\u2019 hands will be tied because of it is considered a purely civil matter and just becomes a money-eating time-wasting matter as executors can block legal attempts to make them act.",
        "background": "If an executor is not willing to perform their duties and does not carry out the deceased\u2019s instructions in their Will, a court should be able to find them in contempt. ",
